[[File:Star_Wars_RPG_All-Temperature_Cloak.jpg|thumb|An illustration of an All-Temperature Cloak.]]
An '''All-Temperature Cloak''' was a wrap around [[Cloak/Legends|cloak]] that protected its wearer from the elements, including severe weather, and hostile conditions. They typically cost one hundred [[Galactic Credit Standard/Legends|credits]] and weighed one and a half [[Kilogram/Legends|kilograms]].<ref name="RPG-Core">''[[Star Wars Roleplaying Game Core Rulebook]]''</ref>

